{"tid":1432215,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣整靚啲中文 URL Links","createTime":"2019-08-08T07:40:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T08:24:36.000Z","uid":264780,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e5a260a663b5b84ccb20ccb7b151b4346d4a2a01","tid":1432215,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:40:24.000Z","msg":"成日大家都想些牙啲<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有中文嘅 URL Links</span></span><br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/光復香港，時代革命\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%EF%BC%8C%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2B4Wvb5rKEvwepesSl%2FR16E%3D&h=0d7a371c\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/光復香港，時代革命</a><br />\n<br />\n通常大家係喺個 browser 嘅 URL Address Bar 度剪剪貼貼：<br />\n1. 全選 Select All (Ctrl + A)<br />\n2. 複製 Copy (Ctrl + C)<br />\n3. 貼上 Paste (Ctrl + V)<br />\n<br />\n出嚟嘅結果通常係一堆<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇唔明嘅數碼</span></span>（唔止連登係噉，邊度都會）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%EF%BC%8C%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25EF%25BC%258C%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E9%259D%25A9%25E5%2591%25BD&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2B4Wvb5rKEvwepesSl%2FR16E%3D&h=0017f1fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%EF%BC%8C%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD</a><br />\n<br />\n上面兩個 Links，雖然 Click 完會去同一頁<br />\n但係第一個 Link 唔使 Click 都知佢想做乜，第二個就要去咗先知<br />\n<br />\n個解決辦法係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好全選</span></span><br />\n因為如果你全選，個 Browser 知道你想複製嘅係 URL<br />\n就會懶醒同你將啲中文做 <span style=\"color: red;\">URL 編碼</span>，又叫百分號編碼<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/百分號編碼\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E7%99%BE%E5%88%86%E8%99%9F%E7%B7%A8%E7%A2%BC&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2B4Wvb5rKEvwepesSl%2FR16E%3D&h=e0af75b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/百分號編碼</a><br />\n<br />\n我嘅做法係喺個 URL Address Bar：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全選淨最頭一個 h 字</span></span>（見下面示意句子）<br />\n2. 複製 Copy (Ctrl + C)<br />\n2.5 人手打個 h 字<br />\n3. 貼上 Paste (Ctrl + V)<br />\n<br />\n<code>h[selected]ttps://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/光復香港，時代革命[/selected]</code><br />\n<br />\n只要你唔係揀晒成條 Address Bar<br />\n個 Browser 就唔會幫你 URL 編碼<br />\n條 Link 就靚返晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀<br />\nWhy when copying a non-English URL from address bar it's URL encoded and not as the text I see (decoded)?<br />\n<a href=\"https://superuser.com/a/1324927\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsuperuser.com%2Fa%2F1324927&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2B4Wvb5rKEvwepesSl%2FR16E%3D&h=421ed342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://superuser.com/a/1324927</a>"},{"pid":"6c674538abc7d9c68392dd7757807ba0580dc489","tid":1432215,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:50:14.000Z","msg":"推到連登啲 Link 都靚返晒"},{"pid":"3c94773573c52adea3cc5862f02449caa0dce7bb","tid":1432215,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:56:36.000Z","msg":"推到政事台啲 Links 都靚返晒"},{"pid":"5bc88f6fce0605ae5feddeed6683034ec88e95b1","tid":1432215,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:02:11.000Z","msg":"推到 Facebook 啲 Links 都靚返晒"},{"pid":"c2c8dbd30715653960f45f2a18a027f7ad42f0cd","tid":1432215,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:08:58.000Z","msg":"推到 IG 啲 Links 都靚返晒"},{"pid":"20034ba98e1e1a00cc90e8bf21215d0a4780ddc6","tid":1432215,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:24:36.000Z","msg":"推到全地球啲 Links 都靚返晒"}]}